{"tid":424862,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Note 8 相片被 DxO Mark 評為 100 「滿分」","createTime":"2017-10-05T07:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T23:09:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b9feb7bd0941726531e537772fabc4dfe5d6bb0","tid":424862,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">被全球認可的 DxO Mark 剛剛發佈了 Samsung Galaxy Note 8 的攝力評分，成功與早前備受好評的 Apple iPhone 8 Plus 打和，讓一眾 Android 用家不用為相機質素而轉會，早算好消息。而且，由於 Galaxy Note 8 的雙相機均備有光學防震，比 Apple iPhone 8 Plus 有更理想的變焦能力，亦被 DxO Mark 評為最出色的「變焦智能手機」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1915000/1918362/20171004_AIR_01_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1915000%2F1918362%2F20171004_AIR_01_1024.JPG&h=6cba68bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1918362/Samsung%20Note%208%20%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%20DxO%20Mark%20%E8%A9%95%E7%82%BA%20100%20%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%BF%E5%88%86%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1918362%2FSamsung%2520Note%25208%2520%25E7%259B%25B8%25E7%2589%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%2520DxO%2520Mark%2520%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%2582%25BA%2520100%2520%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%2588%2586%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%259F&d=S54X9NY0AQwr3%2BNemT3BKTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=89f036d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1918362/Samsung%20Note%208%20%E7%9B%B8%E7%89%87%E8%A2%AB%20DxO%20Mark%20%E8%A9%95%E7%82%BA%20100%20%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%BF%E5%88%86%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F</a></div>"},{"pid":"e62519b8803fe9276eb83782adaf7dbac8f73627","tid":424862,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:07:48.000Z","msg":"在 DxO Mark 的新制度下，擁有雙鏡配置的 Galaxy Note 8 亦理所當然地名列前茅，與備受 DxO Mark 好評的 Apple iPhone 8 Plus 平分秋色，同樣得到 94 總分，可見手機的拍攝質素極為出色。但若看細分，就可以發現兩機的拍攝表現其實有分野。由於 Note 8 的雙 Dual Pixel 光學防震相機，使其在攝影一欄中成功取得 100 分，相對 iPhone 8 Plus 則只有 96 分；但在若考慮影片質素，Note 8 則只取得 84 分，而 iPhone 8 Plus 則有 89 分。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1915000/1918362/20171004_AIR_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1915000%2F1918362%2F20171004_AIR_02_600.jpg&h=be218556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; Samsung Galaxy Note 8 的攝影能力居然取得 100 分，不知道是否可算是滿分呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1915000/1918362/20171004_AIR_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1915000%2F1918362%2F20171004_AIR_03_600.jpg&h=2584c939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&uarr; iPhone 8 Plus 的影片攝錄表現則較優勝；另外，iPhone 8 Plus 相片的散景亦更理想。</span></div>"},{"pid":"7f6075b7f1c1ca1d090ed1f0ef883888e509175e","tid":424862,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"單看分數其實沒有太大意義。大家可以看看 DxO Mark 就 Note 8 的測試樣張，看看大家的想法是否和 DxO Mark 一樣呢？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1915000/1918362/20171004_AIR_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1915000%2F1918362%2F20171004_AIR_04_600.jpg&h=511c20b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1915000/1918362/20171004_AIR_05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1915000%2F1918362%2F20171004_AIR_05_600.jpg&h=cab96cd9&s={SIZE}\